name: 艾达王 王阿姨 Ada Wong Resident Evil 4
description:
Instruction of AdaWong

The improvements in V2 are as follows:

1. I manually eliminated the watermark of the training imgs, now the generated imgs will no longer have a watermark

2. The images generated by V2 are more colorful and no longer blurred like V1

3. V2 is more compatible with realistic checkpoints than V1

Trigger words: Ada_re4, (((beautiful face))), 1girl,black hair, short hair, red sweater, belt, black thigh boots

Lora's weight：0.6~0.8

***1. if the standing pose is always the same, please increase the weight of standing;

***2. Increase the weight of beautiful face can make the face more realistic, but it may deviate from Ada's appearance in the game

AdaWongV2说明

相比V1，V2的改进如下：

1.我手动消除了训练集的水印，现在生成的图片不会再有水印了

2.V2生成的图片色彩更加丰富，不会再像V1一样发白

3.与真人模型的契合度更高，生成的角色更加逼真，尤其是脸部

V2使用说明：

关键词：Ada_re4, (((beautiful face))), 1girl,black hair, short hair, red sweater, belt, black thigh boots

Lora权重：0.6~0.8（不要设置的太高）

***注意事项：1.如果站立姿势总是不变，请提高standing的权重；

2.提高beautiful face的权重可以使脸部更加接近真人，但可能会偏离Ada在游戏中的样貌

————————————————————————————————————————

AdaWongV1说明

兄弟们，新鲜出炉的王阿姨王姐姐来啦~例图在上面，不要用太高的分辨率生成图像，强烈建议使用高分修复，我自己设定的高分修复生成参数如下：

其他信息都在图片里，触发词是Ada_re4。权重可以参考我图片里的，也可以自己尝试，不过如果太高不好换衣服。裸图我给了一张做参考。底模建议KoreanStyle2.5D，这个模型可以很好地生成游戏3D人物，网站如下：

https://civitai.com/models/12975/koreanstyle25d

这个是我做的碍事梨：https://civitai.com/models/25224/resident-evil4-ashley

注：如果想换衣服，就把red sweater和red leotard这两个tag放进负面提示词框框里，衣服的权重也可以稍微调高一点

V2说明

Ada Wong in Resident Evil 4, the trigger word is Ada_re4. Don't generate images at too high resolution, and I strongly recommend using Hires. fix to generate the images, The following picture is for reference：

By the way, you can add fashion girl, KoreanDollLikeness, JapaneseDollLikeness to make Ada more like asian.

Don't set the weight too high or it'll be diffiucult to change her clothes.

Better put red sweater and red leotard into negative prompt if you want to change her red sweater into something else.

The base model is KoreanStyle2.5D which can generate very good-looking 2.5D characters, here is its website:

https://civitai.com/models/12975/koreanstyle25d

Another one of my Resident Evil character works-Ashley：https://civitai.com/models/25224/resident-evil4-ashley
